telegram_bot: Sign up through the Telegram bot
first_reminder: For the Olympics, 30 questions are provided, the first 10 questions are evaluated at 2.1 points, the next 10 questions at 3.1 points, the last 10 questions are evaluated at 5.1 points.
third_reminder: The duration of the Olympics is 1 hour.
fourth_reminder: After the allotted time has expired, for each question that the participant answered, points are awarded, unanswered questions are not evaluated.
fifth_reminder: The top 500 participants who scored the most points will have the opportunity to move on to the 2nd stage.
sixth_reminder: Results can be viewed in the personal account.
resultsDesc: The top 300 participants who scored the most points will move on to the second stage. If you are one of them, you can see the message 'You have moved on to the second stage!' on this page soon. Also, the message will be sent to your phone as an SMS.
